Merge pull request #8 from shinyPy/refactor
Refactor

Revamp service pages and improve SEO metadata
Major UI update for infrastruktur, pabrikasi, and rekayasa-industri pages: content split into text and image columns, added project showcases with Next.js Image components. Enhanced metadata for all main routes with more descriptive titles and Open Graph info. Sitemap now includes lastModified, changeFrequency, and priority for better SEO.

Add pages for Pabrikasi and Rekayasa Industri
Introduces new pages for 'Pabrikasi Moulding' and 'Rekayasa Industri' with tabbed service and project sections. Updates BusinessSolutions and HoverCardGroup components to support navigation to these new pages and improve mobile/desktop UI behaviors.
Update hero slider videos for improved visual content
Refactor BusinessSolutions component and enhance connection speed detection logic

Refactor homepage cards and FAQ animations
Replaced framer-motion with custom CSS animations for FAQ and BusinessSolutions components, improving performance and reducing dependencies. Updated Tailwind config with new animation and keyframe utilities. Removed unused imports and cleaned up page structure.

Add business solutions and collaboration sections
Introduces BusinessSolutions and CollaborationPartners components to the homepage and about page. Adds new infrastructure service and project page, updates metadata for /infrastruktur, and includes new partner and background images. Also refactors FeaturesGrid to remove unused icons and updates homepage layout to use new components.

Revamp homepage with new stats, certifications, and FAQ
Added CompanyStats, Certifications, and FAQ components to the homepage for improved company credibility and user information. Updated AboutContent, FeaturesGrid, and ServicesGrid to reflect new company profile, services, and ISO certifications. Enhanced metadata and map embed for better branding and SEO.
